% =============================================================
% ProGuard references — pivot from EMA to CUSUM.
%
% After EMA-based ProGuard failed (collaborator's experiment +
% our 5 bolt runs: capjjdzxus, sfbaazyhrb, cfhhzaq7sw,
% t3e38hgze5, 3yw2vp6et3 — all showed r_vis drifts too slowly
% for rate-of-change hinge to fire), we redesigned around
% sequential change-point detection (CUSUM).
%
% Key insight: backdoor injection causes CUMULATIVE drift in
% r_vis that is sub-noise per-step but accumulates over 40K
% training steps to a large drop. CUSUM with a FIXED anchor
% accumulates these sub-noise deviations, and a softplus
% relaxation makes the recursion differentiable so gradient
% flows back to model parameters.
% =============================================================

